These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, coffee, juice, milk
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, ship, quad-bike, bus, scooter
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, aconite, balloon-flower, tulip, marigold
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, mystery, adventure, epic, thriller
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is the person drinking milk##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is the person driving the bus##1
 6. the person driving the ship is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 8. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the person who growsaconite is the person watching zombie movies##1
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Beverage         | almond-milk  | sprite    | juice | coffee    | milk  |
| Transport   | ship  | tram | quad-bike | bus | scooter  |
| Flower           | zinnia     | marigold     | tulip  | aconite   | balloon-flower    |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure | epic    | mystery | zombie  | thriller |

