.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, orange, purple, ivory, red
House: futuristic, cottage, ranch-style, tower, farmhouse
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, gardening, singing, woodworking, card-games
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daffodil, amaryllis, rose, poppy
 1. the tower house is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 6. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person who likes purple is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person who growsrose is the person who likes purple##1
10. the person who likes orange is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
12. the person who likes purple is the cottage house##1
13. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Color          | purple        | red | orange     | ivory      | fuchsia  |
| House           | cottage   | ranch-style | farmhouse    | tower | futuristic |
| Hobby   | singing | woodworking     | card-games | sudoku    | gardening  |
| Flower   | rose     | daffodil | bellflower    | poppy      | amaryllis    |

