.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, rose, amaryllis, iris
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: musical, mystery, crime, western, adventure
There 5 different types of food: lime, cranberry, lettuce, orange, irismelon
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, baseball, basketball, cycling, rugby
 1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person eating irismelon##1
 2. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person eating lime is in the middle##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is in the middle##1
 5. the person eating lettuce is on the far right##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
11. the person eating lettuce is the person watching musical movies##1
12. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
13. the person who growsamaryllis is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Flower      | amaryllis          | rose  | aconite       | sunflower     | iris      |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery | adventure | western  | crime   | musical    |
| Food   | cranberry        | irismelon | lime | orange    | lettuce   |
| Sport     | volleyball   | basketball | rugby      | baseball | cycling |

