.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: american, italian, pakistani, german, mexican
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, fonseca, tiparillo, prince, ritmeester
The people have 5 different jobs:  security-guard, lawyer, entrepreneur, analyst, firefighter
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, skateboarding, basketball, skiing, climbing
 1. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the security-guard##1
 2. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the pakistani##1
 3. the lawyer is the fonseca-smoker##1
 4. the security-guard is the dannemann-smoker##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the analyst##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
 9. the analyst is on the left of the american##1
10. the mexican is the entrepreneur##1
11. the italian is on the left of the mexican##1
12. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the firefighter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Nationality          | german        | american       | pakistani | italian   | mexican  |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | tiparillo | fonseca | dannemann   | prince |
| Job   | analyst         | firefighter     | lawyer | security-guard | entrepreneur     |
| Sport     | cycling        | skateboarding        | climbing    | skiing    | basketball      |

