 2. the person who growssunflower is the person driving the bike##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 4. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 5. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 6. the person driving the subway is the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is in the middle##1
 9. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
10. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes pink is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
12. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
