.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, guinea-pig, bird, frog
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: indie, house, disco, r&b, techno
5 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, canasta, mah-jongg, go
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, aristoff, davidoff, fonseca, bluemaster
 1. the fan of techno is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the davidoff-smoker is the fan of disco##1
 3. the owner of the frog is in the middle##1
 4. the fan of indie is the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the person playing go is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 7. the person playing canasta is in the middle##1
 8. the owner of the bird is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 9. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the fan of house##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
11. the fan of indie is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
12. the fonseca-smoker is the person playing billiard##1
13. the owner of the dog is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |
| Pet          | guinea-pig     | bird  | frog | hedgehog     | dog |
| Music-Genre           | indie   | house | techno     | disco | r&b |
