 3. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 7. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
 8. the futuristic house is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is the art-deco house##1
10. the person eating papaya is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
13. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the art-deco house##1
14. the colonial house is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
