5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bluemaster, cain, bongani, pall-mall
 1. the person playing snooker is the british##1
 2. the dutch is the person who likes azure##1
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person playing go##1
 4. the german is the davidoff-smoker##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the davidoff-smoker is the person playing domino##1
 7. the person who likes chestnut is the person playing domino##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the polish##1
 9. the german is on the far left##1
10. the cain-smoker is the person who likes yellow##1
11. the polish is the person playing scrabble##1
12. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the german##1
13. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
14. the person who likes black is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |      4       |     5      |
| Color      | chestnut       | azure   | black        | blue          | yellow      |
| Nationality         | german | dutch | british  | polish | indonesian |
