5 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, frog, turtle, horse
There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, chestnut, apricot, grey, light-blue
 1. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is the person who likes light-blue##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the tower house is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is the victorian house##1
 6. the art-deco house is the person playing chess##1
 7. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 8. the person playing poker is the owner of the frog##1
 9. the person who likes grey is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes apricot is the owner of the turtle##1
11. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
12. the owner of the horse is the person who likes grey##1
13. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |    5    |
| Game          | scrabble | poker  | backgammon      | monopoly   | chess |
| House   | tower   | ranch-style | wooden   | victorian | art-deco   |
