.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, tiparillo, swisher, cain, old-henry
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, colombian, canadian, egyptian, russian
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, volleyball, weightlifting, sailing, surfing
There 5 different types of food: orange, blueberry, corn, grapes, apricot
 1. the colombian is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
 3. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 4. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 5. the indian is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 6. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 7. the colombian is the person eating orange##1
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the indian##1
 9. the person eating apricot is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
11. the person eating grapes is on the left of the russian##1
12. the canadian is the person who's sport is sailing##1
13. the russian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Cigar      | bolivar      | tiparillo       | old-henry         | cain  | swisher |
| Nationality   | canadian  | egyptian | colombian | indian  | russian  |
| Sport   | sailing    | volleyball    | biathlon        | surfing | weightlifting     |
| Food           | blueberry | corn      | orange       | grapes   | apricot   |

