City: london, venice, hannover, nizza, edinburgh
The people have 5 different jobs:  analyst, paramedic, chef, writer, project-manager
 1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the project-manager##1
 3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the writer##1
 4. the australian is on the left of the spanish##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the paramedic is on the left of the australian##1
 7. the indonesian is the analyst##1
 8. the italian is the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the person traveling to venice is in the middle##1
10. the person traveling to london is the person driving the airplane##1
11. the writer is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
12. the australian is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
13. the egyptian is the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
