.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  entrepreneur, analyst, dancer, engineer, electrician
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, blood-red, blue, red, orange
House: ranch-style, palace, wooden, modern, cape-cod
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip, daisy, dahlia, bellflower
 1. the palace house is on the left of the modern house##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 3. the person who likes orange is the person who growssunflower##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growstulip is the dancer##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the wooden house##1
 7. the engineer is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 8. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is in the middle##1
10. the cape-cod house is on the right of the wooden house##1
11. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
12. the person who likes blue is the electrician##1
13. the modern house is on the left of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Job      | dancer | electrician    | analyst   | engineer   | entrepreneur |
| Color   | white    | blue   | orange | red | blood-red  |
