.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There 5 different types of food: mango, cranberry, radish, lemon, lettuce
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, white, purple, aquamarine, amber
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, ritmeester, alhambra, blend, game
5 different games are played: scrabble, domino, poker, bridge, snooker
 1. the person eating radish is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person eating radish is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 4. the person who likes lavender is the game-smoker##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 7. the person who likes purple is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 8. the person playing domino is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person eating mango##1
10. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
11. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1
13. the chaman-smoker is the person eating lemon##1
14. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Food      | cranberry | lemon   | radish    | mango       | lettuce |
| Color   | purple           | white   | amber   | aquamarine       | lavender  |
| Cigar   | ritmeester       | chaman | alhambra | blend     | game   |
| Game     | poker    | domino   | bridge   | scrabble | snooker   |

 